high_descs: Go to the sink that is on your right.
Get the spoon out of the sink.
Turn the opposite direction and go past the fridge, then turn right and face the center of the brown rack.
Put the spoon into the mug on the left of the center shelf of the rack.
Pick up the mug with the spoon in it.
Take the mug and spoon back to the sink.
Put the mug and spoon into the sink, between the glass and the silverware.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug holding a spoon into a kitchen sink.

high_descs: Turn right, move to the sink.
Pick up the spoon in the sink.
Turn around, bring the spoon around to the right, to the wooded rack next to the door.
Put the spoon in the mug on the rack.
Pick up the mug with spoon on the rack.
Turn right, had back towards the main part of the kitchen, across to the sink.
Put the mug with spoon in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a spoon in it, in the sink.

high_descs: go to the sink
take the spoon from the sink
take the spoon to the shelves in the corner
put the spoon in the white mug on the second shelf from the bottom
pick up the cup with the spoon in it
take the cup to the sink
put the cup and the spoon in the sink
anns.task_desc: put a spoon in a mug and put them in the sink
